  "body": "### Component\r\n\r\nAnvil\r\n\r\n### Have you ensured that all of these are up to date?\r\n\r\n- [X] Foundry\r\n- [X] Foundryup\r\n\r\n### What version of Foundry are you on?\r\n\r\nforge 0.2.0 (6abb763 2022-09-08T00:05:15.055944634Z)\r\n\r\n### What command(s) is the bug in?\r\n\r\nforge script --legacy \r\n\r\n### Operating System\r\n\r\nLinux\r\n\r\n### Describe the bug\r\n\r\nWhen I try to deploy my contract (composed of a dozen contracts and libraries), I notice that Anvil starts consuming up to 10GB, saturating my RAM and crashing. \r\n\r\n**Memory consumption when Anvil is running**\r\n![Memory consumption when Anvil is running](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/1005318/189162199-5c76268e-2a25-42d0-adf2-eaa0c2f6b6d9.png)\r\n\r\n**Memory consumption during the deployment of my  contract.**\r\n![Memory consumption during the deployment of my  contract. ](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/1005318/189162672-10afbd4c-8a14-422c-b85e-01c2927594da.png)\r\n\r\n\r\n**Anvil's crash**\r\n![Anvil's crash](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/1005318/189165555-86d9b00d-0138-4426-8ebe-bca2b2d5d9e9.png)\r\n\r\n\r\n**Memory consumption when Ganache (v7.4.3 (@ganache/cli: 0.5.3, @ganache/core: 0.5.3)) is running**\r\n![Memory consumption when Ganache (v7.4.3 (@ganache/cli: 0.5.3, @ganache/core: 0.5.3)\r\n) is running](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/1005318/189166682-a9523959-b22e-4b45-8062-0051623d58a0.png)\r\n\r\n\r\n**Memory consumption after the deployment of my  contract with Ganache (v7.4.3 (@ganache/cli: 0.5.3, @ganache/core: 0.5.3)**\r\n![Memory consumption after the deployment of my  contract with Ganache (v7.4.3 (@ganache/cli: 0.5.3, @ganache/core: 0.5.3)\r\n) ](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/1005318/189166841-07f7b745-d767-4ee2-a9e2-121a08746303.png)\r\n\r\n",
